                <h1 class="mb-0">Shared Hosting Explained For Clients</h1>
                <p class="mb-0">This isn't just another article explaining shared hosting. Instead, I'll break it down from a system administrator's perspective—why you should never use shared hosting, even for a small web application, and what better alternatives exist. If you're looking for affordable hosting solutions, this will be a comprehensive guide, much like my previous article on web development. Let's dive in!</p>
